            <title><![CDATA[Sackboy For PC Is Only $12.59 At Amazon, PS5 Special Edition With Plush Is $50]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/sackboy-for-pc-is-only-12-59-at-amazon-ps5-special-edition-with-plush-is-50/1100-6528342/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
