            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/sackboy-for-pc-is-only-12-59-at-amazon-ps5-special-edition-with-plush-is-50/1100-6528342/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><p>
    <span data-nosnippet="">GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links.</span>
  </p><article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6528342">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>The adorable <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CBNPMX7P?tag=gamespot-promos-20&amp;th=1" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Sackboy: A Big Adventure</a> is now available on PC for just $12.59 (was $60) at Amazon, <strong>one of its lowest prices ever</strong>. It’s offered as a Steam key, though you’ll need to be an <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/prime/pipeline/signup?tag=gamespot-promos-20&amp;tag=gamespot-buybutton-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon Prime member</a> to cash in on the massive discount. If you're not already a member, consider signing up to earn free shipping, access to Prime Video, and other useful benefits.</p><p>Along with support for 4K resolutions, this version of the game supports 21:9 ultra-widescreen setups, runs at up to 120fps, can be played with a variety of gamepads beyond the DualSense, and offers DLSS when played on GeForce RTX graphics cards. That’s a lot of cool features for PC players--and at this rock-bottom price, it’s an easy recommendation for anyone seeking a family-friendly platformer. Our <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/sackboy-a-big-adventure-review/1900-6417610/" data-ref-id="1900-6417610">Sackboy: A Big Adventure review</a> gave the game a solid 7/10, praising its tight controls, catchy soundtrack, and a great variety of platforming challenges.</p><p dir="ltr">"Sackboy is a solid platformer and, despite its rote art style, makes great use of the PS5's enhanced visual and technical performance," wrote critic Mike Epstein. "It's a fun little romp of a platformer, with lots of interesting moments. At times, the visual design can look a bit flat. Even in those moments, though, the tight controls and interesting level layouts create gameplay challenges that make those flaws easy to overlook."</p><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4413102-sackboy-ps4-special-edition-game.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4413102" data-ratio="0.563" data-width="1000" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4413102-sackboy-ps4-special-edition-game.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4413102"></a><figcaption>Sackboy: A Big Adventure Special Edition with Plushie</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1702/17023653/4413102-sackboy-ps4-special-edition-game.jpg"></figure><p>This isn’t the only version of the game getting a price cut ahead of the holidays, as you’ll also find <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%2F%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-games%2Fsackboy-a-big-adventure-special-edition-ps4&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsackboy-for-pc-is-only-12-59-at-amazon-ps5-special-edition-with-plush-is-50%2F1100-6528342%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Sackboy: A Big Adventure Special Edition for PS4</a> discounted to $50 (was $90). Along with a PS4 version of the game (and free PS5 upgrade), the Special Edition includes an adorable Sackboy plushie, making it a great holiday gift. The deal expires on Christmas, so check it out while you can.</p><p>If you’re not interested in the plush, then save yourself some money and pick up the standard edition of <a href="https://howl.link/n7lyi84b1oaq1?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17338201662612?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Sackboy: A Big Adventure on PS5</a> for $20 (was $60). That’s not quite as cheap as the PC version, but if you don’t have a PC that can handle the game, this version is a nice alternative. The price cut is available at both <a href="https://howl.link/n7lyi84b1oaq1?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17338201662612?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Best Buy</a> and <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%2F%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-games%2Fsackboy-a-big-adventure-ps5&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsackboy-for-pc-is-only-12-59-at-amazon-ps5-special-edition-with-plush-is-50%2F1100-6528342%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">PS Direct</a>.</p><h2>Best Sackboy Deals</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CBNPMX7P?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Sackboy: A Big Adventure (PC)</a> -- $12.59 (<del>$60</del>)</li><li><a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%2F%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-games%2Fsackboy-a-big-adventure-special-edition-ps4&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fsackboy-for-pc-is-only-12-59-at-amazon-ps5-special-edition-with-plush-is-50%2F1100-6528342%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Sackboy: A Big Adventure Special Edition with Plushie (PS4 + PS5)</a> -- $50 (<del>$90</del>)</li><li><a href="https://howl.link/n7lyi84b1oaq1?article_name=Gamespot&amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17338201662612?u1=subid_value" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Sackboy: A Big Adventure (PS5)</a> -- $20 (<del>$60</del>) | Also at <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%2F%3Fid%3D225336X1707200%26xs%3D1%26xcust%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fbuy-games%2Fsackboy-a-big-adventure-ps5&amp;p=http%